;; Shared expect helper for commercial_readiness e2e (Issue #1934).
;; Included by concatenating or by paste; kept as documentation of the
;; harness contract. Each commercial_readiness_*.aura inlines a copy so
;; files stay single-load (no include path dependency).
;;
;; Contract for Python e2e_harness:
;;   - print "PASS: <label>" on success
;;   - print "FAIL: <label> expected=... actual=..." on failure
;;   - print "E2E-PASS" iff zero FAIL lines
;;   - print "E2E-FAIL" if any FAIL
